      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEMORY OF MUM (7) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing eighth (20.60) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form at the trip excellent including five wins. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Tough to beat if on-song. BLUE LAKODA (3) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at 13 of 21 starts including five wins but missed the frame latest when fourth (16.69) over 300m at Q Straight. Tends to go well on this box draw. Expected to feature on best form. ROLLING ROYALTY (2) was an effortless winner two back scoring by a neck but could manage only midfield last time when finished 4th and beaten 4.5 lengths at this track (19.98). Likely to play a prominent role. OUTLAW NANCY (1) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
